## For Prospective Students

If you are interested in joining my research group, please email with:
- Your CV
- A brief description of your research interests
- Relevant coursework or projects
- Any papers or projects you have worked on

I work on **hardware verification**, **ML for CAD**, **hardware security**, and **agentic AI energy measurement**. Strong backgrounds in digital design, computer architecture, or machine learning are all relevant.

